        "action": "Let's have a referendum on independence for London",
        "additional_details": "I don't see any problems with London independence that don't already exist in the wider Brexit and Irish border debates.\r\n\r\nhttp://littleatoms.com/london-independence\r\nhttps://www.change.org/p/sadiq-khan-declare-london-independent-from-the-uk-and-apply-to-join-the-eu\r\nhttps://www.ft.com/content/80282496-97a8-11e7-a652-cde3f882dd7b",
        "background": "Despite 60% of Londoners having voted to remain in the EU, it looks like the rest of England & Wales will force through Brexit, fuelling the prospect of further UK break-up. If that happens, we should have a referendum on London leaving the UK.",
